author: Adam Voge
title: Townhome project advances in Blaine
text:
Home / Brief / Townhome project advances in Blaine Townhome project advances in Blaine By: Adam Voge July 24, 2015 12:46 pm 0 A developer’s plan for 45 townhomes is moving forward in Blaine. The city’s Planning Commission last week recommended approval of Anoka-based Paxmar’s proposal for detached single-family townhomes at Parkside North, a single-family subdivision just north of where Woodland Parkway meets 122nd Avenue Northeast.
